        Body Corporate Levies and Sinking Funds: What Sellers of Brisbane Units Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Body corporate finances are one of the most common sources of buyer hesitation and late-campaign renegotiation when selling Brisbane units. Here is what sellers need to disclose and what buyers look for.
      </p>
    </div>
